body:
Refactor container comparison function in py/C++ and py/upb to return enum instead of integer.

The new enum is:
```py
typedef enum {
  kPyUpb_CompareEqual, # formerly return value 1
  kPyUpb_CompareNotEqual, # formerly return value 0
  kPyUpb_CompareError, # formerly return value -1
} PyUpb_CompareResult;
```
